          <div class="testimonial-card__stars" aria-label="5 stars">‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ</div>
          <p class="testimonial-card__quote">"The checklist alone saved me hours. Every document, every booking, every detail ‚Äî all organised in one place."</p>
          <footer class="testimonial-card__footer">
            <strong class="testimonial-card__name">Ana R.</strong>
            <span class="testimonial-card__meta">Philippines ¬∑ Portugal Trip</span>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BLOG PREVIEW -->
  <section class="section section--tinted" aria-labelledby="blog-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section-header">
        <div class="flex-between" style="flex-wrap:wrap;gap:var(--space-4)">
          <div>
            <span class="section-label">Latest Insights</span>
            <h2 id="blog-heading" class="section-title">From the Blog</h2>
          </div>
          <a href="/blog/" class="btn btn--secondary">View All Posts ‚Üí</a>
